# ðŸ”„ GitHub Repo Auto-Mirror Sync

Yeh project aik automated workflow hai jo mere **Main Project** ko mere **Backup Project** ke saath hamesha synchronized rakhta hai. Agar mein aik repo mein code push karta hoon, to woh doosri repo mein khud-ba-khud update ho jata hai.

## ðŸš€ Features
- **Auto-Sync:** Har push par automation chalti hai.
- **Conflict Solver:** `reset --hard` logic use ki gayi hai taakay merge conflicts ka masla na aaye.
- **Secure:** GitHub Secrets aur PAT (Personal Access Token) ka istemal kiya gaya hai.



## ðŸ› ï¸ Setup Instructions

### 1. Token Setup (PAT)
Sab se pehlay aap ko aik **Personal Access Token** generate karna hoga:
- GitHub Settings > Developer Settings > Tokens (Classic).
- Permissions mein `repo` aur `workflow` ko check karen.
- Token ko copy kar len.

### 2. Secret Configuration
- Apni source repository (`main-project`) ki **Settings** mein jayen.
- **Secrets and variables** > **Actions** par click karen.
- `New repository secret` banayen:
  - **Name:** `PAT`
  - **Value:** (Apna copied token paste karen)

### 3. Workflow File
Yeh file is path par honi chahiye: `.github/workflows/sync.yml`

```yaml
name: Sync Repos
on:
  push:
    branches: [main]

jobs:
  sync:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - name: Checkout Source
        uses: actions/checkout@v3

      - name: Mirror to Backup
        run: |
          git config --global user.email "muhammadumer5689@gmail.com"
          git config --global user.name "mumerdevops"

          # Clone Destination
          git clone "https://x-access-token:${{ secrets.PAT }}@[github.com/mumerdevops/backup-project.git](https://github.com/mumerdevops/backup-project.git)" backup-dir
          cd backup-dir

          # Force Sync Logic
          git remote add source-repo "https://x-access-token:${{ secrets.PAT }}@[github.com/mumerdevops/main-project.git](https://github.com/mumerdevops/main-project.git)"
          git fetch source-repo
          git checkout main
          git reset --hard source-repo/main
          git push origin main --force
        env:
          PAT: ${{ secrets.PAT }}
